Juvenile xenopus.Comment: This definition is a guess at the top end (less than 1 year).
Juvenile xenopus.Definition: A xenopus over 90 days old but less than 1 year, with the day of birth defined as day 0 or the stage of being a sexually immature animal. (Adapted from Xenopus ontology: http://purl.org/obo/owl/XAO#XAO_1000010)
